00:04:18.103 --> 00:04:20.740
And what's the area
of circle 2?

00:04:20.740 --> 00:04:26.580
The area of circle 2, it's
pi times its radius.

00:04:26.580 --> 00:04:28.340
And its radius is 1.

00:04:28.340 --> 00:04:31.360
So 1 squared.

00:04:31.360 --> 00:04:34.920
